</g>

<!-- 브랜드 -->
<text x="340" y="38" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Georgia,serif" font-size="11" fill="#a78bfa" letter-spacing="4" opacity="0.8" style="fill:rgb(167, 139, 250);stroke:none;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke-width:1px;stroke-linecap:butt;stroke-linejoin:miter;opacity:0.8;font-family:Georgia, serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:400;text-anchor:middle;dominant-baseline:auto">✦ LUMI TAROT ✦</text>

<!-- 서브 카피 -->
<text x="340" y="298" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Georgia,serif" font-size="14" fill="#f9a8d4" letter-spacing="1" opacity="0.9" style="fill:rgb(249, 168, 212);stroke:none;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke-width:1px;stroke-linecap:butt;stroke-linejoin:miter;opacity:0.9;font-family:Georgia, serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:400;text-anchor:middle;dominant-baseline:auto">그 사람 속마음이 궁금하다면</text>

<!-- 메인 타이틀 -->
<text x="340" y="344" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Georgia,serif" font-size="36" font-weight="700" fill="#f0e6ff" letter-spacing="1" style="fill:rgb(240, 230, 255);stroke:none;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke-width:1px;stroke-linecap:butt;stroke-linejoin:miter;opacity:1;font-family:Georgia, serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;text-anchor:middle;dominant-baseline:auto">무료 타로 리딩 🔮</text>

